The info bite is a short snippet of information shown on either a solid color
or an image with a semi-opaque color on top.

<h2>Rules</h2>

<ul>
	<li>Used in situations where you want to convey short bites of information, possibly in a grid.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Syntax</h2>

<div class="pattern-source">{{> info-bite }}</div>


<h2>Options</h2>

<ul>
	<li>The image and therefore the <code>&lt;div class="image"&gt;...&lt;div&gt;</code> is optional.</li>
</ul>


